<br>
I got to thinking.. many of our 61+ spells are upgrades to older spells... perhaps we need to look into the proper configuration of these new spell elements (notes, words, bindings, etc) combined with our existing pre-60 spells in order to create new ones.<br>
<br>
Of course this is a ludicrous amount of combines on top of the already daunting number of items we have to play with, but it's just a thought.  I've done a few combines, but I've had somewhat limited playtime of late.<br>
<br>
A little nudge from VI on this would be remarkably awesome.<br>
<br>
-Taji<br>
